records.addlTxt: Def called asking why he had a warrant for his case. Def stated when he looked up his case on CCAP after he got released from custody on October 21, 2022, it didn't show that there was a court date for this case. I informed the defendant that on October 4, 2022 the hearing was scheduled in court, which he was present for, and notice was sent out the same day. The hearing was scheduled for a Second Appearance on October 24, 2022 at 3:00 PM and due to him being appointed a public defender, the hearing was changed to a Preliminary Hearing - Schedule or Waiver on the same date and time. Def was told to contact his attorney and have him submit something to our office to request a new court date.
Sent to GLSO on October 27, 2022.
